HEADWORD: Lycoperdon
<hw>Ly`co*per"don</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <ety>[NL.,
from Gr. <?/ wolf + <?/ to break wind.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
